R.P. Scherer Inc said it registeredwith the Securities and Exchange Commission a proposed publicoffering of 1.2 mln shares of convertible exchangeablepreferred stock at 25 dlrs a share.    In addition, the company said it is offering 200,000preferred shares to Richard Manoogian, a Scherer director at 25dlrs a share. Manoogian said he will buy the 200,000 shares.    Proceeds from the offering will be used to repay debt andto fund research and development, it said.    Underwriters are led by Goldman, Sachs and Co. Reuter&#3;